{"tid":174621,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"打丁正確時間","createTime":"2017-03-27T02:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T06:27:29.000Z","uid":92638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39485cb1b8bff577c7bee28ab37f72b3cde3e13a","tid":174621,"uid":92638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:58:47.000Z","msg":"有冇人發覺如果係訓前打完丁之後果段時間都好精神，訓極都訓唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但如果係朝早起身先打，去到晏就夜晚就會好攰，唔係好想郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以經過我精密既推測，一係就唔打，一打就要係黃昏時段打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一黎唔洗擔心晏啲有野要做，二黎又有時間緩沖一下個情緒，夜晚就有教好訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n誠邀巴打今晚放工放學我地黃昏六點正同步打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c70e0490c9843d40f858cf697381ee8e1cbcb0","tid":174621,"uid":94474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:11:43.000Z","msg":"?!"},{"pid":"354f6691804f818ef166f7fdd1b3a204de2a4c68","tid":174621,"uid":94474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:12:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>?!</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e6652ff988b98b848ba724fa55c3b5af919bc0","tid":174621,"uid":92638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:13:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>?!</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家未夠鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899cd2122e9980d2616f54596db28be277eb52a2","tid":174621,"uid":46609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T06:27:29.000Z","msg":"幾有趣，但嘗試戒丁中"}]}